(1, 'About Us', '<ul><li><strong class=\"ql-size-large\">Our Platform and Unique Experiences</strong></li></ul><p><br></p><p>At NAVEGA, we don’t just rent boats – we provide a gateway to unique and unforgettable experiences on the water. We are a global platform that connects people who are passionate about the sea with boat owners in a wide variety of destinations. NAVEGA was born from a vision of sharing the love of boating, and for this reason we offer our customers the opportunity to explore the world from a different perspective: on board a boat, with complete freedom and the reassurance of being supported by a professional service.</p><p><br></p><h3><strong class=\"ql-size-large\">Carefully Selected Owners with High Standards</strong></h3><p><br></p><p>Our commitment to quality begins with the careful selection of the boat owners who join our platform. Every owner in the NAVEGA community is vetted to ensure they meet <strong>strict standards of experience, safety, and service</strong>. We collaborate only with owners who demonstrate professionalism and a true passion for boating. In this way, we ensure that every vessel available on our platform is in optimal condition and that each rental unfolds safely and satisfactorily for the customer.</p><h3>Our Core Values</h3><p>NAVEGA is guided by four core values that shape everything we do:</p><ul><li><strong>Trust:</strong> We foster honest and reliable relationships between customers and owners, building a community where integrity is paramount.</li><li><strong>Safety:</strong> Safety is our top priority in every experience. We promote responsible practices and require compliance with all boating regulations to protect everyone involved.</li><li><strong>Transparency:</strong> We value transparency throughout the entire process. We provide clear and complete information—no surprises or fine print—about pricing, conditions, and the details of every service.</li><li><strong>Excellence:</strong> We have an unwavering commitment to excellence. This is reflected in the quality of customer service we provide and in our constant effort to exceed expectations in every detail of the experience.</li></ul><p><br></p><ul><li><strong class=\"ql-size-large\">NAVEGA’s Mission and Vision</strong></li></ul><p><strong class=\"ql-size-large\"><span class=\"ql-cursor\">﻿</span></strong></p><p>Our mission is to provide each client with an unforgettable boating experience, combining exceptional service with a truly personalized touch on every rental. We strive to ensure that every trip booked through NAVEGA becomes a positive and lasting memory, defined by fun, adventure, and the peace of mind that comes from being in good hands.</p><p>Our vision is to be the world’s leading platform for boat rentals, renowned for offering unparalleled nautical experiences and unsurpassed customer service. We aspire to continuously innovate and to expand our global community of boating enthusiasts, creating an ecosystem where service excellence and a passion for the sea come together to consistently deliver extraordinary experiences to our users.</p>', 'About Us', 'About Us', '2019-09-14 10:25:58', '2025-03-12 04:43:09'),
